TextBody:
Hi James,

Engineering got back to me and asked me to collect some new information. A recording of deleting the computers and how they are still there after a short while along with the developer console opened.
They also mentioned that on the computers that were last seen longer than 2 months in your case, those computers may be reporting erroneously to the server and the last seen is not changed.
The recommended action is to make sure the agents are uninstalled.
Please let me know when you have availability for a remote session.

Thank you,
Eduard Nut
